'''Apocia''' was a kind of tree whose white wood was used to make luxury furniture. It was native to the planet [[Bethal]]. They were very vulnerable to a [[Greddleback termite/Legends|greddleback]] attack and took over two hundred years to mature.<ref name="AJ4">{{JournalCite|4|Galaxywide NewsNets}}</ref> The desk in [[Dooku/Legends|Dooku's]] private shuttle was made out of polished apocia wood. In [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]] [[Thrackan Sal-Solo]] had splendid apocia chair in his [[Office of Corellian President|office]] on [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]].<ref name="Legacy of the Force: Bloodlines">''[[Legacy of the Force: Bloodlines]]''</ref> [[Chief of State (Galactic Alliance)|Chief of State]] of [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] [[Cal Omas]] also had apocia wood chairs in his [[Chief of State's Suite|office]].<ref name="Legacy of the Force: Sacrifice">''[[Legacy of the Force: Sacrifice]]''</ref>

